.\" ###### Setup ############################################################
.Dd May 26, 2026
.Dt make\-dbeaver\-configuration 1
.Os make\-dbeaver\-configuration
.\" ###### Name #############################################################
.Sh NAME
.Nm make\-dbeaver\-configuration
.Nd Make DBeaver Configuration from HiPerConTracer Database Configuration Files
.\" ###### Synopsis #########################################################
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm make\-dbeaver\-configuration Ar database\_configuration\_file Ar ...
.br
.Op Fl j | Fl \-join
.Nm make\-dbeaver\-configuration
.Op Fl h | Fl \-help
.Nm make\-dbeaver\-configuration
.Op Fl v | Fl \-version
.\" ###### Description ######################################################
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm make\-dbeaver\-configuration
takes HiPerConTracer database configuration files and merges them into the DBeaver configuration file.
.Pp
.\" ###### Arguments ########################################################
.Sh ARGUMENTS
The following arguments may be provided:
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It Ar database\_configuration\_file Ar ...
Specifies one or more HiPerConTracer database configuration files as input.
.It Fl j | Fl \-join
Join with existing DBeaver configuration. The existing configuration is
searched in the following directories:
.Bl -bullet
.It
.Pa $HOME/.local/share/DBeaverData/workspace6/General/.dbeaver
.It
.Pa $HOME/\%snap/\%dbeaver\-ce/\%current/\%.local/\%share/\%DBeaverData/\%workspace6/\%General/\%.dbeaver
.El
.It Fl h | Fl \-help
Prints command help.
.It Fl v | Fl \-version
Prints program version.
.El
.\" ###### Exit status ######################################################
.Sh EXIT STATUS
The
.Nm
tool exits with 0 on success, and >0 in case of an error.
.\" ###### Examples #########################################################
.Sh EXAMPLES
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It make\-dbeaver\-configuration hipercontracer\-database.conf
.It make\-dbeaver\-configuration $HOME/test4hpct\-*\-*.conf \-\-join
.It make\-dbeaver\-configuration hipercontracer\-database.conf \-\-join
.It make\-dbeaver\-configuration project1\-database.conf project2\-database.conf project3\-database.conf \-\-join
.It make\-dbeaver\-configuration \-\-version
.It make\-dbeaver\-configuration \-h
.El
